data.name: Apex_Description
data.value: Apex legends is the hottest Battle Royal game to hit the gaming scene. For you to excel in the game, it’s crucial you learn the guns and understand each unique legend and their abilities. With these abilities, you can build your reputation and be among the few experts in the game. Try our Apex Legends coaching service and start winning. Our experienced coaches will help you build on your strengths so you can get kills and carry your team to a deserved victory.

data.name: CSGO_Description
data.value: Counter-Strike: Global Offensive is one of the most fast-paced, breathtaking and competitive team FPS games in the industry. If you’re looking to improve your counter strike skills or choose the right loadout under pressure, our professional Counter-Strike coaches are here to help you. Your gaming experience doesn’t matter, with E-Sport Academy; you’ve got something to learn.

data.name: Dota2_Description
data.value: This is one of the most intense, most played E-sports games. You need skills in tweaking hero builds, winning your lane, pushing down towers amongst others, if you wish to dominate ranked players. Just like in any competitive game, all levels of players can get stuck and unable to progress further in the game. This is where our DotA2 coaching services come in. Our coaches are experienced in the game and will help you navigate your way to the top of the list of experts in DotA2. They’re not just gamers but excellent teachers who will give you the hands-on knowledge you need.

data.name: Fortnite_Description
data.value: Fortnite is a new online battle royale survival game introduced in 2017. Though new, it has attracted more than 100 million players in less than 2 years. As a new game, people are still figuring it all out so this could be the perfect opportunity for you to step up your game and be among the few experts. When you start building your Fortnite reputation early on, you can become one of the best players in the E-Sport industry. Our experienced Fortnite coaches are there to guide you through the high-energy and action-packed nature of the game, so you don’t get overwhelmed.

data.name: LoL_Description
data.value: League of legends, one of the most popular and extremely competitive online battle arena, has many aspects and approaches to it. The game can be overwhelming and challenging to navigate through to the top, but don’t worry, our league of legends coaching service has got you covered. Our extensively experienced and dedicated LoL coaches will provide you with bespoke lessons depending on your playing level. If you’re aiming to reach your goal, our coaches will use their knowledge and skills to get you there.

data.name: Wow_Description
data.value: To be the best in this game, you should understand your game level and all the essential aspects of the game. The game is stressful for new players and requires constant maintenance of high concentration and extended ability to deal with unknown and challenging situations. Never to worry; our coaches are experts that are successful as competitive WoW players and are eager to give you important advice and insights that will immensely improve your performance.
